{"tid":13932,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張志剛：梁游唔係鬼","createTime":"2016-11-30T09:42:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T11:17:11.000Z","uid":5195,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7a4822e0919acd3bd80b80c4c22616649ac8b1e","tid":13932,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:42:30.000Z","msg":"張志剛今日喺《明報》撰文，反駁有民主派話青政係「鬼」嘅觀點，話香港地方細，同愛國陣營機構有過連繫、幾乎無人可以避免，仲話而家唔少反共、反水貨反蝗人士，曾經係左派中人或新移民，仲以已故支聯會主席司徒華為例，話佢喺《大江東去》一書交代同中共關係，又話民主派大佬同中共交往一定比梁游多，反問華叔、民主派又係咪「鬼」？<br />\n<br />\n有民主派中人一路睇一路笑，話有張志剛「認證」梁、游唔係鬼，咁佢兩個人係「人」定「鬼」，大家心中有數！"},{"pid":"8dad7458f82efc22283ce5758c455c3b4854d435","tid":13932,"uid":1096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:53:12.000Z","msg":"共狗認證呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f70828076999a7e717d22b37d59ebd1556feea","tid":13932,"uid":40763,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T09:57:21.000Z","msg":"條撚屌專登加多句挑撥離間<br />\n我而家更加確信梁游唔係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f64ffb35eb1fc25e2abb0586ae3d5350a51298","tid":13932,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:02:49.000Z","msg":"匯點嗰堆垃圾就肯撚定係鬼啦"},{"pid":"813a8faf98d2dad2e647e99bfdd40d4635cb5f00","tid":13932,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:05:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共狗認證呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁肯定係鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7bec330f778ce4577125691a68bec68809b3c0a","tid":13932,"uid":8465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:06:23.000Z","msg":"邊個反暴力邊個就係鬼。"},{"pid":"811b8597ef2d6d677e8daf6a02aa8673a236612a","tid":13932,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T10:13:51.000Z","msg":"民主派中人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br